channel.title: Server Isn't Working Online *Hamachi*
channel.description: I have been able to play on my server locally, but when I tried making it online with Hamachi recently it always give me this error, " No response from server. Please try another world." What do I do?

item.title: Server Isn't Working Online *Hamachi*
item.dc:creator: @RSMASTER RSMASTER
item.description:
@RSMASTER wrote:

did you change the clients ip to your hamachi ip?

if not, you should be able to change in client.java
search for 127.0.0.1 replace with your hamachi ip
